2006年12月，迪士尼發佈首批《孟漢娜》周邊，包括服飾、珠寶、玩具和玩偶，而服飾系列複製了-{zh-hans:汉娜·蒙塔娜;zh-tw:孟漢娜;}-在這部劇身穿的衣服<ref name="taleoftwotweens"/>{{sfn|Mayes-Elma|2011|p=177}}<ref name="bitebarbie">{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/lifestyle/2007/11/19/2007-11-19_bite_me_barbie_disneys_hannah_montana_ta-2.html |title=Bite me, Barbie! Disney's ''Hannah Montana'' takes over as most wanted toy |last=Pesce |first=Nicole Lyn |work=Daily News|publisher=Tribune Publishing|date=2007-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071222043409/http://www.nydailynews.com/lifestyle/2007/11/19/2007-11-19_bite_me_barbie_disneys_hannah_montana_ta-2.html|archive-date=2007-12-22|url-status=dead|access-date=2020-12-21}}</ref>。劇集還開發一系列電子遊戲，首款電玩《孟漢娜》於2006年10月5日在[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]發行<ref name="videogame">{{cite news|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2006/10/23/hannah-montana-review|title=''Hannah Montana'' Review|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=Ziff Davis|last=Thomas|first=Lucas M.|date=2006-10-24|access-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317054702/https://www.ign.com/articles/2006/10/23/hannah-montana-review|archive-date=2014-03-17|url-status=live}}</ref>。2008年2月，《孟漢娜》品牌系列收益不錯，迪士尼因此召開「80人、全平台的國際會議」來討論其未來<ref name="grooveback">{{cite web|url=http://www.portfolio.com/news-markets/national-news/portfolio/2008/04/14/Disneys-Evolving-Business-Model|title=How Mickey Got His Groove Back|last=Taro Greenfeld|first=Karl|work=Portfolio.com|publisher=American City Business Journals|date=2008-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080608092713/http://www.portfolio.com/news-markets/national-news/portfolio/2008/04/14/Disneys-Evolving-Business-Model|archive-date=2008-06-08|url-status=dead|access-date=2020-12-21}}</ref>。迪士尼向股東提供的2008年度報告列出此品牌為公司增長有主要作用{{sfn|Mayes-Elma|2011|p=174}}。[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]估計《孟漢娜》品牌系列在2008年底價值10億美元{{sfn|Mayes-Elma|2011|p=174}}。這檔節目是迪士尼頻道是商業性最成功的經銷權影集<ref name="commercial">{{cite news|url=https://www.marketplace.org/2016/03/24/ode-hannah-montana-business-model/|title=An ode to the ''Hannah Montana'' business model|last=Menendez|first=Sarah|work=Marketplace|publisher=American Public Media|date=2016-03-24|access-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221064425/https://www.marketplace.org/2016/03/24/ode-hannah-montana-business-model/|archive-date=2020-12-21|url-status=live}}</ref>。

===可能的衍生劇===
2011年，比利·雷·希拉曾表示想製作[[前傳|前傳]]<ref name="2011prequel">{{cite news|url=https://hollywoodlife.com/2011/06/22/billy-ray-cyrus-hannah-montana-prequel/|title=So Strange: Billy Ray Cyrus Wants To Make A ''Hannah Montana'' Prequel, Even Though He Claimed The Show 'Ruined' His Family!|work=Hollywood Life|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|date=2011-06-22|access-date=2020-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222012745/https://hollywoodlife.com/2011/06/22/billy-ray-cyrus-hannah-montana-prequel/|archive-date=2020-12-22|url-status=live}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Hollywood Life|好萊塢生活}}》於2020年報導稱[[Disney+|迪士尼+]]在討論可能會製作麥莉·史都華當流行歌手成名的前傳，並打算找另名童星來飾演史都華<ref name="2020prequel">{{cite news|url=https://hollywoodlife.com/2020/01/31/billy-ray-cyrus-hannah-montana-prequel-would-do-it/|title=Billy Ray Cyrus Reveals ''Hannah Montana'' Prequel Is In The Works & He'd 'Do It In A Heartbeat'|work=Hollywood Life|last=Wilson|first=Samantha|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|date=2020-01-31|access-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228084203/https://hollywoodlife.com/2020/01/31/billy-ray-cyrus-hannah-montana-prequel-would-do-it/|archive-date=2020-12-28|url-status=live}}</ref>。比利·雷·希拉再次表示自己願意參與，但有報導稱麥莉·希拉沒有興趣<ref name="2020prequel"/>。

